<div id="p235" class="blockpost rowodd">
	<h2><span><span class="conr">#7&nbsp;</span><a href="viewtopic.php?pid=235#p235">2008-05-27 16:54:13</a></span></h2>
	<div class="box">
		<div class="inbox">
			<div class="postleft">
				<dl>
					<dt><strong><a href="profile.php?id=89601">dave</a></strong></dt>
					<dd class="usertitle"><strong>Editor</strong></dd>
					<dd class="postavatar"></dd>
				</dl>
			</div>
			<div class="postright">
				<h3> Re: Discussion of BEP 9: The Metadata Extension</h3>
				<div class="postmsg">
					<p>The BEP allows both base32 and 40-byte hex.&nbsp; <br />I don't have much opinion on the matter.&nbsp; &nbsp;<br /><br />From uTorrent, you can right-click on any torrent and select &quot;copy magnet URI&quot;.&nbsp; The generated URI uses the base32 encoding.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="clearer"></div>
